column4: <content>[Briefhoofd: Brod Gallery]. Korte inhoud: Antwoord op brief FG [niet bewaard] met vraag om informatie over een vermelding in The Connoisseur. De kunsthandel beschikt over drie schilderijen van Pieter Brueghel [sic]. Zendt reproducties van 'Return from the Inn', ex. collectie Sir Francis Glyn en van 'The Wedding Feast' en een brochure.</content>
<parts.title>1 zw/w foto met stempel Christie's, Photograph by A.C. Cooper; nr. 725394.</parts.title>

<parts.title>[Brochure] The Brod Gallery, London; A recent Acquisition, Pieter Brueghel the Younger (Brussels 1564- 1638 Antwerp), 'The Return from the Inn'; Panel [...], Provenance [...], Exhibitions [...], Literature, Marlier p. 418, N° 2; [Notitie FG]: ' Sold. Another version in Toronto.'; [knipsel 1]: The Return from the Inn; [ knipsel 2]: A Recent Acquisition. Pieter Brueghel the Younger [...], 'A Village Wedding Feast', panel 26 by 41 inches, 66 by 104 cm.</parts.title>

<parts.title>[3 Kleurplaten]. Brod Gallery, Pieter Brueghel the Younger, The Return from the Inn, Panel: 76 x 104 cm, signed, [Dubbel]; Brod Gallery, Peter [sic] Brueghel the Younger (1564-1638), [zonder titel= Wedding], Panel: 261/4 x 401/2 inches.</parts.title>
